				<td colspan="2"><span>Think most peeps would suggest you putting a lot on dex/sta, but it really depends.  Coz if you wanna be a soloing bard, sta is not the major factor, as long as you are not going to melee; but dex help us to minimize missing notes a lot.
<br />

<br />
It's just my opinion, coz I put some into int/wis to make larger mana pool myself, well not a big different to others.
<br />

<br />
And kitty city dont have ALL songs we use, but some common songs that you can buy from Antonia cities.  PoK is the greatest place you looking for, you could find all or most songs (coz I havent make the checklist) there from 5 vendors.
<br />

<br />
Just my 2cp</span></td>
